      <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-<%= color %>-800">
        This is specifically for Testing/Feedback Purposes only. Please use your current tools: PWRStation, salesforce etc as you normally would and do not depend on this site.
      </h3>
      <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-<%= color %>-600">
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
          <li>
            This site is NOT ready to replace those tools yet.
          </li>
          <li>
            You can not break salesforce or any of your current tools by testing this site.
          </li>
          <li>
            This site works entirely independently of current systems though it may have current information.
          </li>
          <li>
            Data will be deleted/reset on this site randomly. Do not depend on information from this site.
          </li>
          <li>
            Please give us as much feedback about this site as possible. You will be required to use this site in the future when we shut down some of the current tools.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>